-------------------------------------------------------------------
NEW: First configure, make and make install the library libxpcockpit

cd ../libxpcockpit

If you cloned from git first run these in order to populate all needed automake/
autoconf files:
autoreconf
automake --add-missing
autoreconf

Then type:
./configure
make
make install

Then jump back to this directory here.
